radio:
    play sound click
    choice:
        "The airwaves flash their ankles at you. Which of the many, many slutty frequencies will you get down and dirty with?"
        "[What else? Tune yourself into 'Sissy FM' and watch the feminising results take effect immediately] <span class='prompt'>[[-1 ACTION]]</span>":
            play sound spendAction
            set data.game_map.inHouse false
            run transition intro_home
            add_stat actions -1
            set data.global.radioDone true
            clear_dialog
        "[Turn off the radio] <span class='prompt'>[[BACK]]</span>":
            jump home
    stop music
    play ambient amb_radio 1
    set data.ghost.sissyFM true
    wait 2000
    run transition_study true
    talk sissy talk "Welcome, beta, to Sissy FM~ The most feminising show on the airwaves~"
    talk orb talk "Sissy FM, really?"
    talk lovely talk "I've heard of this method! It's effective in up to ninety percent of cases!"
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk nasty talk "My mate Dave once recorded one of these but it was about pissing yourself and the absolute geezer played it on my mate Darren's gramophone while Darren was asleep and guess what..."
        "What?":
            talk nasty talk "Was too effective. Silly twat shit himself!"
            talk lovely talk "Disgusting! Please make her stop talking, Orb!"
            talk orb talk "I hold no responsibility for Nasty Girl's words and deeds. Keep me out of this."
            talk nasty talk "I'm going to do it to *you* next Lovely Lady!"
            talk lovely talk "Scream!"
    clear_dialog
    "The radio crackles to life. A smooth feminine voice, like melted caramel, is spooned into your ear..."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk sissy talk "*You* are a little faggy boy~"
        "[Nod] \\"You know it bud.\\"":
            add data.radio_nods 1
        "\\"I am a bit, I suppose?\\"":
            add data.radio_neutral 1
        "\\"Uhhh, logical fallacy. That was an ad hominem attack and you know it, mam.\\"":
            add data.radio_debate 1
    choice:
        talk orb talk "Is this working. I don't think this is working. I'm almost certain radios don't work this way."
        "It would work a lot better if you didn't interrupt, Orb!":
            talk orb talk "Doubtful, but fine. I'll leave you and your time wasting alone."
            talk lovely talk "Up to ninety percent of cases, Orb!"
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk sissy talk "You *love* to be a beta~"
        "\\"Yup.\\" [Nod] \\"So true bestie.\\"":
            add data.radio_nods 1
        "[Scribble 'love to be a beta' down on your notepad] \\"Hmm yes.\\"":
            play sound write
            add data.radio_neutral 1
        "\\"Source?\\"":
            add data.radio_debate 1
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk sissy talk "You *love* to be weak~ You *want* to be *dominated*~"
        "[Nod] \\"You know me better than I do, Sissy FM.\\"":
            add data.radio_nods 1
        "\\"I guess so yes. Well. Maybe.\\"":
            add data.radio_neutral 1
        "\\"Again, wrong. Only thing I want to do is win this debate, peon.\\"":
            add data.radio_debate 1
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk sissy talk "You *smell* like a girl~ The *men* around you can smell it~ That you have the *musk* of a faggot~"
        "[Nod] \\"Absolutely. I smell so girly.\\"":
            add data.radio_nods 1
        "\\"I smell of *something*.\\" [Sniff your armpit] \\"Blech!\\"":
            add data.radio_neutral 1
        "[Scoff] \\"Did you not go to debate school? Are you even trying?\\"":
            add data.radio_debate 1
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk sissy talk "You have a *tiny* penis~"
        "[Nod] \\"I really do. It's like an acorn.\\"":
            add data.radio_nods 1
        "\\"I have a pretty normal size one actually.\\"":
            add data.radio_neutral 1
        "\\"But a large IQ. Your point?\\"":
            add data.radio_debate 1
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk orb talk "I'm not convinced this is going to work Ghost. Shall we find something else to do with our time?"
        "Damn. This sucks. I thought this would work.":
            run skip
        "It's fine. I knew this wouldn't work. I was only doing it for a bit. [Lie]":
            run skip
        "No! No! It has to work! I just need to try harder! [Tense your muscles and clench your eyes and strain your head so hard you get a headache]":
            run skip
    clear_dialog
    run transition_fromStudy generic_winter
    if (> $data.radio_nods 3):
        choice:
            talk orb talk "Actually all that nodding burned off so many calories that your left tit kind of shrunk and is now slightly smaller than your right tit."
            "No! Not lefty! Oh me oh my! Am I becoming a fascist!?":
                choice:
                    talk orb talk "What? No? Ghost, did you just invent a new type of cup-size based phrenology?"
                    "[Mournfully shake your head] More like SS hypno... [Turn off the radio] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                        play sound spendAction
                        talk orb talk "What???"
                        unlock_achievement sissy
                        stop ambient 1
                        jump goToGameMap
    if (> $data.radio_neutral 3):
        choice:
            "A chill runs up your spine. Something is... different..."
            "[Check and realise all the calorie intensive listening you've been doing has actually made your tits slightly smaller, if anything] \\"No! No! Fuck!\\" [Punch the wall really hard and hurt your hand] \\"Owie!\\"":
                run transition_pain
                choice:
                    talk nasty talk "Damn. Radio kind of shit, huh?"
                    "[Sob] So bad! So so bad! [Turn off the radio] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                        play sound spendAction
                        unlock_achievement sissy
                        stop ambient 1
                        jump goToGameMap
    if (> $data.radio_debate 3):
        choice:
            talk orb talk "I'm unsure why you were so insistent on arguing with the radio. It can't hear you, Ghost."
            "Wrong. The brainless whore inside the radio heard every one of my scathing rebuttals. [Shout at the radio] \\"Consider yourself debated bitch!\\" [Smash the radio to bits with a chair] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                play sound spendAction
                unlock_achievement sissy
                stop ambient 1
                jump goToGameMap
    else:
        if $data.ghost.used_hrt:
            choice:
                talk orb talk "How about we just let the oestrogen you took do it's work instead of talking to the radio, yes?"
                "Fine. Fuck me for being impatient I guess... [Turn off the radio] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                    play sound spendAction
                    unlock_achievement sissy
                    stop ambient 1
                    jump goToGameMap
        else:
            choice: 
                talk orb talk "Let's focus on finding an actual solution to your lack of oestrogen. One that doesn't involve talking to the radio, yes?"
                "Fine. Fuck me for being impatient I guess... [Turn off the radio] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                    play sound spendAction
                    unlock_achievement sissy
                    stop ambient 1
                    jump goToGameMap